Package org.neo4j.test.rule

Class RandomRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.test.rule.RandomRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.junit.rules.TestRule
    public class RandomRule
extends Object
implements org.junit.rules.TestRule
    Like a Random but guarantees to include the seed with the test failure, which helps greatly in debugging. Available methods directly on this class include those found in RandomValues and the basic ones in Random.
